title:
Summer Vegetable and Chicken Quinoa Minestrone
ACTIVE TIME
20m
TOTAL TIME
4h
8 servings
directions: Add all ingredients on list up to chicken to your slow cooker. Stir to combine, then add in chicken breasts. Cook on low for 4 hours.
Stir in beans and spinach. Cook for 5 more minutes.
Add balsamic vinegar and taste; adjust salt and pepper as needed.
Tip: Use chopped frozen carrots and onions to save time.
ingredients: One 15-ounce jar roasted red peppers, coarsely chopped
One 15-ounce can cannellini beans, drained and rinsed
2 (heaping) cups chopped fresh spinach, coarsely chopped
Salt and freshly ground pepper to taste
